  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A soft contact lens integrating a Sensor is placed on subjects with high intraocular pressure
      (IOP) after administration of an IOP-lowering drug to investigate the device's capacity to
      detect the induced IOP reduction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
